<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 22 at 10:03AM EST  by NWS Albany</headline>
<description>...Icy Spots Still Possible through Midday...
Temperatures in the higher terrain of southern Vermont and the
Berkshires remain in the low to mid 30s and with fog lingering
through midday, untreated roads and sidewalks may continue to be
slippery. Use caution if traveling.</description>
